<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/tailwindcss/2.2.19/tailwind.min.css"
    />
    <title>Home Page</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="flex justify-between px-16 py-4 bg-gray-900 text-white">
      <div class="text-2xl">OurApp</div>
      <div>
        <input type="text" class="border rounded px-2" placeholder="Username" />
        <input
          type="password"
          class="border rounded px-2"
          placeholder="Password"
        />
        <button class="bg-blue-600 rounded px-2 py-px">Login</button>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main class="flex p-32 gap-32">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-thin">Remember Writing?</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Suscipit
          nostrum commodi dolor accusamus autem. Sunt similique maiores nihil
          eaque repellat voluptatem itaque eveniet odio sapiente tempore in
          deserunt, temporibus delectus reprehenderit labore earum aspernatur
          cupiditate incidunt veritatis ut. Commodi assumenda blanditiis saepe
          maiores corrupti at ea sunt, ipsum fugit voluptatibus.
        </p>
      </div>
      <form class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <input
          type="text"
          class="border rounded px-2 w-72"
          placeholder="Username"
        />
        <input
          type="password"
          class="border rounded px-2"
          placeholder="Password"
        />
        <input type="email" class="border rounded px-2" placeholder="Email" />
        <button class="text-white block bg-green-600 rounded px-2 py-2">
          Signup
        </button>
      </form>
    </main>
    <hr />
    <footer class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 text-center">
      Copyright Â© 2023 OurApp. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
